## Install
```
pip install pyupdog
```
## Run

```

UPDog.py --vcf test_data/200518_A00748_0027_AHLKFCDRXX.vcf.gz \
--proband_id test_sample \
--ped test_data/200518_A00748_0027_AHLKFCDRXX.ped \
--output results/200518_A00748_0027_AHLKFCDRXX \
--min_dp 25 \
--min_gq 15 \
--min_qual 20 \
--p_value 0.001 \
--block_size 1000000 \
--min_variants_per_block 100 \
--min_blocks 2 \
--min_proportion 0.01


```
